<language en>
<h3>ServoStiK</h3>
Controller board based on ATMEGA644P with  bioloid and RX bus headers, servo-style headers for several I/O, and FTDI driver.

<h5>Features Include</h5>
<ul>
  <li>Control RX & AX servos at the same time. Board automatically configures at startup.</li>
  <li>Sync-Read capability, for higher bandwidth.</li>
  <li>10 I/O, including 8 analog inputs and 2 hobby servo outputs.</li>
  <li>Seperate power buses for AX and RX servos.</li>
  <li>Small size: 3.125"x1.125".</li>
</ul>

